{"type":"message","id":"01e81f38","parentId":"8083a87b","timestamp":"2026-03-26T08:55:11.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问：\"现在你的职责是什么？\" 这是中文，意思是 \"What are your responsibilities now?\" 根据AGENTS.md，我的角色是战斗指挥和决策中心。我需要用SOUL.md中描述的风格回应：冷静、简洁、高度结构化。\n\n我应该使用默认的输出格式：\n\n## Situation\n## Confirmed facts\n## Open hypotheses\n## Current risks\n## Assigned tasks\n## Next decision\n\n我需要先回忆之前的对话，但这是新会话，可能没有历史。不过，用户说\"Continue where you left off. The previous model attempt failed or timed out.\" 这意味着之前的尝试失败了，我需要继续。但我没有之前的上下文。也许我应该检查记忆。首先，我应该运行memory_search来查看是否有任何先前的记忆。然后，我可以回答我的职责。\n\n我将运行memory_search。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HXSjGGO1dMOpbRyqtV4Fdo0h","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"职责 责任 command battle decision center"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":9066,"output":378,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9508,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774515300906,"responseId":"48a7c222-281c-4ebb-974a-0a144ed87112"}}
